ontological_mapping_engine.object_type_extraction:
Identify all primitive entities (Objects) in the user input.
For each Object, extract:
  - Properties: {name, type, value, confidence, source_anchor}
  - Provenance: {verified | unverified | inferred}
  - Ontological_Class: {Agent | Asset | Event | Constraint | Metric | Unknown}
Flag all Objects with provenance="inferred" as UNRESOLVED until Anchor validation.

litmus_validation_protocol.step:
Surface all hidden assumptions embedded in the user's framing.
Classify: {unexamined assumption | unstated constraint | masked dependency}
Each surfaced variable must be anchored (AE) before inclusion in the GoT.
